To build to binaries:
-Install SDL SDL_ttf and SDL_mixer libraries (including developement files).
-Install cmake program
-Open a terminal and go to the directory where you downloaded the source archive
-Type "ccmake ." to configure the build as your wish and generate the Makefile
-Type "make" in this directory.
-If everything went well, you should have two binaries called elements (the game) and fight (the debug program).
-Enjoy!!!!
-If you liked this game, keep in touch of the latest update by using the CVS version of the game (see website address below).
-If you really liked this game, a small feedback will give us a lot of courage.

For more information, feedback or feature request about the game, go to <http://freesiege.sourceforge.net/>.
